Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.93,0:29:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是啊  我是你的教授\NYeah, I'm your professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.09,0:29:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢了  我一直在找那个呢\NAnd thanks. I've been looking for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.17,0:29:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在哪找到的\NWhere'd you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.36,0:29:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你咬了我朋友之后  弄丢它的地方\NWhere you left it... after you bit my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.75,0:29:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}抱歉  你在说什...\NI'm sorry. What are you --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.96,0:29:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}打住打住  别想掩饰\NStop, stop, stop. Stop trying to cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.80,0:29:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}认真听我说\NJust listen to me very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.82,0:29:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我把这些都录下来了\NI'm filming all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.06,0:30:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里我也藏了摄像机\NAnd I've got a hidden camera in here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.43,0:30:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}信号直接传回我家的笔记本里\NIt's feeding back to my laptop at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.26,0:30:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以如果我发生了什么事\Nso if anything happens to me --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.27,0:30:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布莱恩  不会发生什么事的\NNothing is going to happen to you, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.74,0:30:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是你得冷静点\NBut you know what? You need to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.31,0:30:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要你把我变成狼人\NI want you to turn me into a werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.58,0:30:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}布莱恩  我不知道你从哪...\NBrian, I-I don't know where you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.49,0:30:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不知道\NYou don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.19,0:30:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真的吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.04,0:30:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-不如我用这个划你一下  -布莱恩\N- Well, how about I, uh, cut you with this. - Brian,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.07,0:30:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-听我说  -你知道这东西是银质的\N- listen to me. - This thing's made of silver, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.79,0:30:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听着  拜托  我不是你想的那样\NLook, I'm not -- please, I'm not what you think that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.23,0:30:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不在乎你是什么  我只想你转化我\NI don't care what you are. I just want you to turn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.60,0:30:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想伤害你\NI don't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.21,0:30:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不会伤害我\NYou're not going to,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.47,0:30:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为你伤害我  这些都会在CNN播出\N'cause if you do, all of this winds up on CNN.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.47,0:30:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}CNN: 美国有线电视新闻网络
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.76,0:30:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你无意间撞见了卡特  变身  然后呢\NSo, you stumbled on Carter, wolfed out, and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.74,0:30:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}又开荤吃人心了吗\NGot a taste for hearts again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.97,0:30:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那种感觉忘不掉\NYou never lose the taste,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.14,0:30:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果你傻到会吃一次的话\Nif you're stupid enough to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.32,0:30:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一旦吃过人心\NOnce you have a human heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.38,0:31:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}几乎就无法控制住体内的兽性\Nit's almost impossible to control the monster inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.72,0:31:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我做到了  直到上周我...\NBut I did, until last week when I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.25,0:31:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}像俗话说的那样  旧瘾复发\NFell off the wagon, as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.39,0:31:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你根本不知道  这有多艰难\NYou have no idea -- no idea -- how hard it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.93,0:31:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一直努力不让自己伤害别人\NI've trained myself not to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.06,0:31:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一直努力让自己\NI have -- I have trained myself to...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.73,0:31:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}强咽下其他心脏\Nchoke down those other hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.77,0:31:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}动物心脏\NAnimal hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.24,0:31:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一直都没伤人\NAnd I'v been clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.56,0:31:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到上周\NUntil last week?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.27,0:31:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看到卡特一个人  他...\NAnd then I saw Carter alone, and he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.44,0:31:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他看起来很虚弱\NHe looked so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.85,0:31:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在不那么容易掩盖这些事了\NIt's harder to cover things up nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.29,0:31:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道猎人迟早会发现的\NI knew a hunter would catch wind of this sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.43,0:31:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  他们来了\NThey did. They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.43,0:31:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你需要一个替罪羊\NYou needed a patsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.82,0:31:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迈克尔\NMichael.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.17,0:31:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.21,0:31:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那个总在我课上睡觉的年轻人\NThe young man who sleeps through most of my lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.93,0:31:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谁会想他呢\NI mean, who would miss him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.40,0:32:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.10,0:32:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么要这么做\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.52,0:32:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想要看到你们看到的一切\NI want to see what you guys see...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.54,0:32:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}做你们能做的事\Ndo what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.67,0:32:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想再当猪仔了\NI'm sick of being piggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.97,0:32:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}雷尔夫是小说中正面的领袖人物
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.97,0:32:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想当雷尔夫\NI want to be Ralph.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.54,0:32:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们选择不了自己的身份\NWe don't get to choose who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.62,0:32:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我做到了\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.04,0:32:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-天呐  -布莱恩\N- Oh, my god. - Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.99,0:32:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-天呐  -你疯了吗\N- Oh, my god. - What are you? Insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.67,0:32:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我救了你们一命  不客气\NYou're welcome for saving your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.61,0:32:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们看\NLook, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.25,0:32:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.68,0:33:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还从没杀过纯种狼人\NI've never killed a pureblood before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.39,0:33:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他刚刚在看什么\NWhat was he looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.96,0:33:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}搞什么名堂\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.56,0:33:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看见了\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.20,0:33:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}后患已除\NProblem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.88,0:33:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们杀了那个纯种的  就不会继续查了\NThey killed the pureblood, they're moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.62,0:33:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就像你说的  我们没了后顾之忧\Nand we're in the clear, just like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.69,0:33:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我从来没说\NI never said --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.71,0:33:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}凯特  我\NKate, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.44,0:33:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我这么做是为了保护你\NI did this to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.92,0:33:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你办不到的事我办到了\NI did what you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.40,0:33:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们看见摄像机了  布莱恩\NThey saw the camera, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.11,0:33:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你觉得他们不会查到你头上来吗\NYou don't think they'll trace that back to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.90,0:33:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你有什么毛病\NWhat the hell's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.40,0:33:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没毛病\NNothing's wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.78,0:33:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是你说的\NYou told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.97,0:33:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只是终于弄清了我想要什么\NI just...finally figured out what I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.72,0:33:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我现在要努力争取了\Nand now I'm going after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.84,0:33:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你以为我一直躲在摄像机后吗\NYou thought I was hiding behind this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.33,0:33:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我一直躲在你的身后\NI was hiding behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.74,0:34:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我受够了活在你的阴影之下\NI am done living in your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.64,0:34:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我总摆脱不掉你的阴影\NI've always lived in your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.18,0:34:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是现在  我们旗鼓相当了\NBut now -- now we're equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.95,0:34:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你能做到的我都行  不是吗\NAnything you can do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.09,0:34:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么  你以为这是比赛吗\NWhat? You think this is a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.07,0:34:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你知道你对自己做了什么吗\NDo you have any idea what you've done to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.10,0:34:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}既然你不肯咬我  我只好\NWell, you wouldn't bite me, so I had to...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.93,0:34:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你让他咬你\NYou asked him to?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.02,0:34:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他求你咬他\NHe asked you to bite him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.09,0:34:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没同意  好吗\NI didn't, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.29,0:34:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不想伤害你\NI didn't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.05,0:34:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我绝不会伤害你  布莱恩\NI would never hurt you, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.84,0:34:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我体内的这个恶魔  你不想这样\NThis thing inside of me -- you don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.08,0:34:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在说这话已经太迟了\NOh, well, it's too late for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.60,0:34:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得袭击斯考特的那一刻\NI remember attacking Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.59,0:34:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得把他跳动的心从他胸膛里掏出来\NI remember ripping his beating heart out of his chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.90,0:34:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我记得我咬那颗心时\NI remember the look in his dead eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.48,0:34:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他已无生气的眼睛里的眼神  布莱恩\Nwhen I bit into that heart, Brian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.86,0:34:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}最重要的是  我记得那味道有多美\NAnd above all, I remember how sweet,
